Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Fabric Softener and Conditioners Market

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the fabric softener and conditioners market will witness a CAGR of 4.96% for the forecast period. Rising product innovations and emergence of new players are the two major factors driving the growth of fabric softener and conditioners market.

Fabric softener and conditioners are used for laundry purposes. Fabric softener and conditioners are the chemical ingredients that are used to condition, cleanse and soften the fabric. These are used at the time when the laundry is being rinsed in the washing machine. Fabric softener and conditioners smell floral in nature and retain the gentleness of the fabric. Today, a number of fabric softener and conditioners are available in the market. There is a stiff competition in this sector.

Rising demand for fabric softener and conditioners that help to retain the softness, increases the shelf life and prevents wrinkle formation is fostering the growth of market. Rising personal disposable income, increasing spending on clothes and a wide range of choice of products to be chosen from is further propelling the growth of fabric softener and conditioners market.

However, exposure to health and environmental hazards owing to the overuse of fabric softener and conditioners will pose a major challenge to the growth of the market. Lack of usage of fabric softener and conditioners for millennial population will restrict the scope of growth for this market.

